{"data":[{"date":"09:40 04/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/nhung-thong-tin-thu-vi-ve-cac-doi-gop-mat-tai-tu-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 g\u1eedi t\u1edbi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00e0 n\u01a1i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi 6/14 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n (chi\u1ebfm t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 42.85%), Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 2/5 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n (40%), ch\u00e2u \u00c1, ch\u00e2u Phi v\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c B\u1eafc - Trung M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u00e0o.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng tin th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng tin th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Thong-tin-thu-vi-ve-cac-doi-gop-mat-tai-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n* Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup (t\u00ednh t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Li\u00ean X\u00f4 tan r\u00e3).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng A (Nga, Uruguay) v\u00e0 G (Anh, B\u1ec9) sau khi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. B\u1ea3ng B v\u00e0 H kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u00e0o \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u1eb7p Uruguay, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina (4-3, v\u00f2ng 1/8) v\u00e0 Peru (1-0, v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* T\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch to\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u00ednh sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 Uruguay v\u00e0 B\u1ec9, Croatia to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110an M\u1ea1ch tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Uruguay\" title=\"Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/da-bai-bo-dao-nha-hlv-uruguay-no-tung-bung.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Uruguay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch to\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u00ednh trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n* Trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Brazil (5), Uruguay (2), Anh v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p (1) l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 Brazil v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2002.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u00e0 Brazil (Nam M\u1ef9), B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n duy nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u1eeb c\u00e1c khu v\u1ef1c kh\u00e1c nhau g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, g\u1ed3m Anh (ch\u00e2u \u00c2u), Panama (B\u1eafc - Trung M\u1ef9), Tunisia (ch\u00e2u Phi) v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (ch\u00e2u \u00c1).<br />\r\n<p>* N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh theo ph\u00e2n nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1eb1m trong  nh\u00f3m 1 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1ed3m Nga (ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0), Brazil, Ph\u00e1p, B\u1ec9, 3 \u0111\u1ed9i thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m 2  g\u1ed3m Anh, Croatia v\u00e0 Uruguay, nh\u00f3m 3 ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n duy nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y  \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi dung do Brazil o tu ket\" title=\"B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/191516-bi.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u1ec9 \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1eafm gi\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>* B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World  Cup 2018 (12 - \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i), Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t (6 - \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 9 t\u1ea1i  gi\u1ea3i).</p>\r\n<p>* Trong c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Nga c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh cao nh\u1ea5t (28.8),  sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 Brazil (28.6), Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Uruguay (28.1), Croatia (27.9), B\u1ec9  (27.6), Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Anh (26).</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-tu-ket-world-cup-2018-nhung-thong-tin-can-biet-465-190344.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/lich-thi-dau-tu-ket-world-cup-2018-nhung-thong-tin-can-biet.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-tu-ket-world-cup-2018-nhung-thong-tin-can-biet-465-190344.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft</span><br />\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup 2018 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 g\u1eedi t\u1edbi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"884","checkdouble":"190347"},{"date":"09:39 04/07","title":"C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng g\u1ecdi t\u00ean ai?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/golden-boot-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 World Cup, ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ebd trao nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 5 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng sau gi\u1ea3i, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng d\u00e0nh cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng hay th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1982. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Paolo Rossi v\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u0169ng trong n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, Rossi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Italia gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/golden-boot-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao d\u1ef1a theo y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n, c\u00e1c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n1. Ai ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ea7n \u00edt penalty h\u01a1n (trong th\u1eddi gian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c)<br>\r\n2. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o h\u01a1n<br>\r\n3. C\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u00edt h\u01a1n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Top c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018:<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>  </strong>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:\n solid black .5pt;mso-border-themecolor:text1;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:\n 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"1\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"6\" style=\"border:solid black 1.0pt;mso-border-themecolor:\n  text1;mso-border-alt:solid black