n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/yerry-mina-phat-bieu-sau-tran-colombia-vs-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mua Willian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 Anthony Martial theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Telegraph \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Juan Mata b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Willian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mua Willian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/chelsea-chi-ban-willian-cho-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Willian c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng song Mata th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, b\u1edfi M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e1 tr\u00e1i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00f2n vai.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mang v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 Willian t\u1eeb Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Mata. Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o ch\u00ed n\u00f3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Mourinho s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea9y Mata ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWillian c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Conte. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn gi\u1eef im l\u1eb7ng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Willian cho MU n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Martial</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mua Willian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 Anthony Martial theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Telegraph \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n n\u1ebfu Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u00ean.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea san sang trao doi giua Willian va Martial\" title=\"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa Willian v\u00e0 Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-306-MU-va-Chelsea-sap-trao-doi-Bom-tan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ea3 Willian n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-khong-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-189958.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Willian</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn v\u1ee5 Willian, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 Martial ra \u0111i. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Mourinho th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u1ee5 trao \u0111\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Martial \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. Mourinho ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"882","checkdouble":"190349"},{"date":"10:14 04/07","title":"Aubameyang c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Sokratis","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/aubameyang-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-den-sokratis.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sokratis, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Dortmund c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Sokratis</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal, HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Laurent Koscielny d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng c\u00f2n Per Mertesacker mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sokratis h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sokratis h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/aubameyang-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-den-sokratis.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Sokratis</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSokratis l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-thu-3-172-190220.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn mua Sokratis th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span>, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 17.6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111eo l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 5. \u1ede Arsenal, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi 2 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Aubameyang v\u00e0 Henrikh Mkhitaryan, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p \u1edf Dortmund.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Sokratis duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Aubameyang tin Sokratis l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sokratis, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Dortmund c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aubameyang noi ve  Sokratis\" title=\"Aubameyang n\u00f3i v\u1ec1  Sokratis\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/auba.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aubameyang n\u00f3i v\u1ec1  Sokratis</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi anh \u1ea5y nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb Arsenal, anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Sokratis c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Emirates, t\u00f4i tin anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui m\u1eebng khi Sokratis \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cSokratis l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, anh \u1ea5y t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf c\u1ea3 CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG. T\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Arsenal, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Sokratis \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Arsenal \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"881","checkdouble":"190350"},{"date":"10:30 04/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Forsberg n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/nguoi-hung-forsberg-noi-gi-khi-dua-thuy-dien-vao-tu-ket.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Emil Forsberg ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Emil Forsberg</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emil Forsberg ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Emil Forsberg ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Emil-Forsberg-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Thuy-Dien-vs-Thuy-Sy-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng treo b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Ricardo Rodriguez v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f2n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ph\u00fat 66, Emil Forsberg tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ed5i h\u01b0\u1edbng khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Sommer b\u00f3 tay.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Forsberg gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 1-0. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-thuy-sy-vs-thuy-dien-421-190298.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</span> gi\u00fap Forsberg v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Anh \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Forsberg h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Emil Forsberg ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Forsberg noi ve tran Thuy Dien vs Thuy Sy\" title=\"Forsberg n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/nguoi-hung-forsberg-noi-gi-khi-dua-thuy-dien-vao-tu-ket.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Forsberg n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. H\u00f4m nay Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u1ede pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i tung ra m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"880","checkdouble":"190351"},{"date":"10:58 04/07","title":"Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian cho MU v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/chelsea-chi-ban-willian-cho-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mua Willian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 Anthony Martial theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Telegraph \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Juan Mata b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Willian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mua Willian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/chelsea-chi-ban-willian-cho-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Willian c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng song Mata th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, b\u1edfi M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e1 tr\u00e1i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00f2n vai.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mang v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 Willian t\u1eeb Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Mata. Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o ch\u00ed n\u00f3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Mourinho s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea9y Mata ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWillian c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Conte. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn gi\u1eef im l\u1eb7ng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Willian cho MU n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Martial</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mua Willian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 Anthony Martial theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Telegraph \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n n\u1ebfu Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u00ean.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea san sang trao doi giua Willian va Martial\" title=\"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa Willian v\u00e0 Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-306-MU-va-Chelsea-sap-trao-doi-Bom-tan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ea3 Willian n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-khong-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-189958.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Willian</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn v\u1ee5 Willian, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 Martial ra \u0111i. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Mourinho th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u1ee5 trao \u0111\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Martial \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. Mourinho ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"879","checkdouble":"190352"},{"date":"11:12 04/07","title":"Arsenal b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n \"r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t\" Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/12/18/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Andre Gomes n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Andre Gomes</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Wilshere ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ra s\u00e2n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Andre Gomes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Andre Gomes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/14/Arsenal-muon-mua-Andre-Gomes-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Adre Gomes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery \u0111ang nh\u1eafm r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Lucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Sampdoria hay Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Andre Gomes n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Gomes, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Arsenal chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates. Barca \u0111\u00f2i 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 Arsenal ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/2-doi-bong-thanh-london-dai-chien-vi-sao-barca-172-184107.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Andre Gomes</span>, nh\u01b0ng Arseal \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng Emery h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Gomes \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Andre Gomes l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Andre Gomes kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1\u00a0b\u1ecb, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Andre Gomes\" title=\"tien ve Andre Gomes\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/16/MU-va-Man-City-vao-cuoc,-Andre-Gomes-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n Andre Gomes cho Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 khi Iniesta ra \u0111i th\u00ec Barca c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Gomes, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Barca h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 3 t\u00e2n binh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, bao g\u1ed3m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Stefan Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"878","checkdouble":"190353"},{"date":"11:16 04/07","title":"Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \"bom t\u1ea5n\" 43 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/22/man-city-sap-cong-bo-bom-tan-43-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City mua Jorginho th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, t\u1edd Guardian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Jorginho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/napoli-xac-nhan-man-city-chuan-bi-no-bom-tan-172-188493.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City quan t\u00e2m Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli</span>. HLV Pep Guardiola \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u00e0 \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Etihad.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jorginho\" title=\"Jorginho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/3/15/4-ngoi-sao-co-the-thay-the-Carrick-o-MU-hinh-anh-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cu\u1ed9c th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City mua Jorginho th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, t\u1edd Guardian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ng\u00f4i sao sinh\u00a0n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Man City s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Jorginho, h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 43 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Napoli \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng Man xanh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p BL\u0110 Napoli \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang theo Jorginho trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Man xanh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Jorginho, Pep s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Serie A, anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Napoli.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00f3ng Man City mua Jorginho v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 43 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"N\u00f3ng Man City mua Jorginho v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 43 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/22/man-city-sap-cong-bo-bom-tan-43-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jorginho l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva, ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u01b0\u1edbc sang s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Jorginho, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 MU v\u00e0 Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Man City \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i\u00a0b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"877","checkdouble":"190354"},{"date":"11:02 04/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 4/7: M.U quan t\u00e2m sao tuy\u1ec3n Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/ngay-hom-nay-47.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (4/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>M.U quan t\u00e2m sao tuy\u1ec3n Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Matteo Darmian mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0, v\u00e0 Juventus c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Torino. MU bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng Darmian \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n k\u00fd ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mario Mandzukic, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 47, tin n\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 47, tin n\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/mu-mua-mario-mandzukic-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mario Mandzukic</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMandzukic ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Croatia sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup v\u1eeba qua. Anh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y v\u00e9 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft sau khi th\u1eafng 3-2 tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat penalty c\u00e2n n\u00e3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho r\u1ea5t th\u00edch Mandzukic n\u00ean mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 l\u00e0m t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng cho MU h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Gi\u1eefa 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean Mario Mandzukic (Juventus) v\u00e0 Marko Arnautovic (West Ham), MU \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0.</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois \u00fap m\u1edf d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real sau Wold Cup</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Thibaut Courtois cho bi\u1ebft, anh s\u1ebd ch\u1edd cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi World Cup 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n v\u1edbi gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 con c\u00e1i - nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i Madrid. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nghi ng\u1ea1i Courtois c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Courtois c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-nang-nac-doi-chuyen-toi-madrid-vi-mot-dieu-172-190264.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/courtois-nang-nac-doi-chuyen-toi-madrid-vi-mot-dieu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-nang-nac-doi-chuyen-toi-madrid-vi-mot-dieu-172-190264.html\">Courtois n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</span><br>\r\n<span>\u0110ang chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 - Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Madrid v\u00e0 \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm Schmeichel \"con\" thay th\u1ebf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois ra \u0111i, Kasper Schmeichel s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7. \"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ec7n\" 31 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i World Cup d\u00f9 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay v\u00f2ng 1/8. C\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin AS Roma c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m cho Schmeichel \"con\".</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool s\u0103n Mina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo Fotomac, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tranh gi\u00e0nh trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Colombia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a The Reds l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao v\u00ec Barcelona kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 47 MU quan t\u00e2m sao tuy\u1ec3n Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 47 MU quan t\u00e2m sao tuy\u1ec3n Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-47-MU-quan-tam-sao-tuyen-Croatia-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mina</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Emery s\u0103n \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo Independent, HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Arsenal chi ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Gomes, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch \"thanh l\u00fd\" c\u1ee7a Barcelona. Hi\u1ec7n Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 Wilshere ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<h2>M.U c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3</h2>\r\n<p>M.U x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lee Grant \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Stoke City. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Grant kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 35 tu\u1ed5i k\u00fd v\u1edbi M.U b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m. Lee Grant \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Sam Johnstone, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh tr\u1ebb v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o West Brom v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 6,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLee Grant l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, sau Fred v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot. T\u1ea1i M.U, Lee Grant s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 3 sau David de Gea v\u00e0 Sergio Romero. Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Lee Grant t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Sheffield Wednesday, Burnley hay Derby County. \u1ede Stoke City, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Jack Butland.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-lee-grant-172-190317.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/Chinh-thuc-MU-mua-thu-mon-Lee-Grant-chuyen-nhuong-tu-do-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-lee-grant-172-190317.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Man Utd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh ai-c\u0169ng-kh\u00f4ng-bi\u1ebft-l\u00e0-ai</span><br>\r\n<span>Manchester United ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai n\u0103m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 35 tu\u1ed5i.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"876","checkdouble":"190355"},{"date":"11:26 04/07","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u1ebft s\u1eb9o d\u00e0i qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch x\u00f3a m\u1edd c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/4/du-am-anh-vs-colombia-vet-seo-dai-qua-khu-nguoi-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0110T Anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m v\u1edbi Colombia, s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 bi quan cho h\u1ecd. Nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Colombia ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ni\u1ec1m vui sau c\u00f9ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u:\u00a0</strong>Anh 1-1 Colombia (pen 4-3)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n:<br>\r\n- Anh:</strong> Kane (57')<br>\r\n<strong>- Colombia: </strong>Mina (90+3') </div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nQu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111au th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1996 (tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u2013 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 th\u00edch ch\u1ea5m 11m), \u0110T Anh m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m. M\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd. Tam s\u01b0 tr\u1ebb trung l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi vi\u1ebft n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t s\u00e2u \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00eam qua, Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Colombia 4-3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i Moscow \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 25,6 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a 5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m l\u00e0 24,6. Nghe qua c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3\u2026 sai sai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Colombia V\u1ebft s\u1eb9o d\u00e0i qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch x\u00f3a m\u1edd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Colombia V\u1ebft s\u1eb9o d\u00e0i qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch x\u00f3a m\u1edd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Du-am-Anh-vs-Colombia-Vet-seo-dai-qua-khu-va-cach-xoa-mo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Anh vs Colombia v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Euro 1996 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, Anh m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng khi \u201c\u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang\u201d c\u00e2n n\u00e3o. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, bi\u1ebft bao n\u1ed7i \u0111au ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh. Nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eeb c\u1ef1 ly 11m t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n song l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t: \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i World Cup 1990 v\u00e0 Euro 1996, Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup 1998, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea1i Euro 2004 v\u00e0 World Cup 2006 r\u1ed3i Italia t\u1ea1i Euro 2012. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Anh ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn t\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay \u0111\u00e3 52 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Beckham Euro 2004\" title=\"David Beckham Euro 2004\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/David-Beckham-Euro-2004.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eebng b\u1ecb \u00e1m \u1ea3nh b\u1edfi penalty</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u ng\u1ea1i 11m. Nh\u01b0 David Beckham ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng bay t\u00edt \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u kh\u00f4ng ai r\u00f5 khi b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa penalty \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Euro 2004.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ea3 11m b\u1ecb h\u1ecfng v\u00e0 n\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n d\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Colombia l\u00e0 v\u00ed d\u1ee5 r\u00f5 n\u00e9t. Trong th\u1eddi gian hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i c\u00e2u gi\u1edd t\u1eeb Colombia. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i \u201c\u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang\u201d c\u00e2n n\u00e3o, l\u1edbn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u khi b\u00f3ng l\u0103n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Colombia tuong thang dc Anh\" title=\"Colombia tuong thang dc Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Colombia-tuong-thang-dc-Anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Colombia c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 Anh tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t 11m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u1edf ph\u00eda sau. Ch\u00ednh c\u1ef1u trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng l\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m khi c\u00f9ng Anh b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c n\u0103m 1996. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Southgate l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng, gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tan v\u1ee1 sau ch\u00ednh c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian qua \u0111i, 22 n\u0103m sau, l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh Southgate l\u00e0 HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean xua tan quan ni\u1ec7m r\u1eb1ng lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m l\u00e0 tr\u00f2 may r\u1ee7i. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n l\u1eabn t\u00e2m l\u00fd \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 t\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Southgate Euro 1996 miss penalty\" title=\"Gareth Southgate Euro 1996 miss penalty\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Gareth-Southgate-Euro-1996-miss-penalty.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Southgate t\u1eebng c\u00f9ng \u0110T\u00a0Anh g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKieran Trippier, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean sau tr\u1eadn: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a khung th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n n\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c, \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i tin v\u00e0o tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/henderson-dt-anh-da-tap-da-penalty-rat-ky-469-190329.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/henderson-dt-anh-da-tap-da-penalty-rat-ky.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/henderson-dt-anh-da-tap-da-penalty-rat-ky-469-190329.html\">Henderson: \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 penalty r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9</span><br>\r\n<span>Jordan Henderson, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng penalty c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 5 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110T Anh b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 11m, ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t Jordan Henderson \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t hay th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David Ospina c\u1ee7a Colombia \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, Tam s\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa cho tai n\u1ea1n \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ec1u cao 1m85 c\u1ee7a Jordan Pickford b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 3, ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Everton \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ee9u tinh c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Carlos Bacca tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Eric Dier \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n\u201d, Pickford n\u00f3i sau tr\u1eadn. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n cao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t b\u1edfi t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Anh thang penalty\" title=\"DT Anh thang penalty\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/du-am-anh-vs-colombia-vet-seo-dai-qua-khu-nguoi-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tam s\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Southgate ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9, Southgate r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean v\u1ebft s\u1eb9o d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng thay v\u00ec tr\u00e1nh n\u00e9, \u00f4ng d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi n\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDanh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i d\u1ef1a theo nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho lo\u1ea1t \u201c\u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang\u201d tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta hay n\u00f3i \u201cThao tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i th\u00ec sa tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed5 m\u00e1u\u201d. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh th\u1ea1o nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 11m hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c, s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ef1 d\u01b0ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y. Ni\u1ec1m vui t\u1ea1i Moscow l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed5 ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. M\u00e0n \u201c\u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang\u201d th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia v\u00ec th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u2026<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/colombia-vs-anh-01-tieu-xao-sai-lam-va-nhung-dac-trung-lam-nen-tran-cau-sieu-kich-tinh-421-190343.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Colombia 1-1 (pen 3-4) Anh: Ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o, sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-anh-tren-cham-11m-421-190321.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau \u0111\u00eam l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-colombia-giai-thich-ly-do-that-bai-truoc-anh-421-190345.html\">HLV Colombia gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-tran-colombia-vs-anh-421-190339.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-noi-gi-sau-khi-cung-nuoc-nha-thay-doi-lich-su-421-190322.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi c\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"875","checkdouble":"190356"},{"date":"07:05 04/07","title":"Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/thuyen-truong-thuy-si-giai-thich-nguy-nhan-that-bai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia, Eric Dier \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khen ng\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t.</h2><h2>Dier khen ng\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Colombia v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Harry Kane trong hi\u1ec7p hai. Tuy v\u1eady, Colombia c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tay v\u1eeba khi ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede hai hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, Colombia l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n khi t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua th\u00eam b\u00e0n n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Dier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/dier-noi-gi-sau-cu-sut-quyet-dinh-dua-dt-anh-vao-tu-ket-world-cup.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Eric Dier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Colombia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 Eric Dier cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 sau khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua tr\u1edb tr\u00eau v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00eam qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;B\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 h\u00f4m qua l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb suy s\u1ee5p v\u00e0 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng \u00fd ngh\u0129 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh sau b\u00e0n thua v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eadt ra c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n t\u00e2m l\u00fd cho t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Dier chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eric Dier l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1eef nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 penalty th\u1ee9 5 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\" target=\"_blank\">Colombia vs Anh</span> v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn h\u01a1i hi\u1ec1n. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Ospina \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tay v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng may m\u1eafn l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebft l\u1ed9 sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, Dier kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u00fat lo l\u1eafng khi g\u00e1nh tr\u00ean vai tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><em>&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc m\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ghi b\u00e0n sau khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 \u01a1n tr\u1eddi l\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh:</strong><br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\"><em>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-trong-ngay-dt-anh-pha-dop-de-vao-tu-ket-469-190319.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Anh ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-anh-tren-cham-11m-421-190321.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau \u0111\u00eam l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Colombia 1-1 (pen 3-4) Anh (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</em></div>\r\n<em> <br>\r\n<br>\r\n</em>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"874","checkdouble":"190328"},{"date":"07:55 04/07","title":"Gareth Southgate: \"Xin l\u1ed7i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0!\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/gareth-southgate-xin-loi-chung-toi-chua-muon-ve-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate sau khi c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Colombia v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u00e1m \u1ea3nh h\u1ecd su\u1ed1t c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c. V\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ea3i Colombia nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n nh\u01b0ng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh, ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng, Tam S\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup sau 12 n\u0103m v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/gareth-southgate-xin-loi-chung-toi-chua-muon-ve-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi! Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua thi\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn trong th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn tinh th\u1ea7n, \u00fd ch\u00ed v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1eaby s\u1ef1 \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1edbi m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;H\u00f4m nay qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1ea1m qu\u00ean n\u00f3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung cho ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft. Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u, v\u1eady n\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00ec tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3, \u0111ang v\u00e0 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra l\u1ecbch s\u1eed cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh. V\u00ec sao \u01b0? \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 xin l\u1ed7i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd!&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a Tam S\u01b0 ti\u1ebfn xa nh\u1ea5t trong v\u00f2ng 28 n\u0103m v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea5m h\u1ecd m\u1ed9ng m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-anh-tren-cham-11m-421-190321.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau \u0111\u00eam l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-noi-gi-sau-khi-cung-nuoc-nha-thay-doi-lich-su-421-190322.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi c\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/trippier-len-tieng-nhan-loi-ve-ban-go-hoa-cua-colombia-469-190323.html\">Trippier l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Colombia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/dier-noi-gi-sau-cu-sut-quyet-dinh-dua-dt-anh-vao-tu-ket-world-cup-469-190331.html\">Dier n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau c\u00fa s\u00fat quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Anh v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/henderson-dt-anh-da-tap-da-penalty-rat-ky-469-190329.html\">Henderson: \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 penalty r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"873","checkdouble":"190330"},{"date":"07:18 04/07","title":"Dier n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau c\u00fa s\u00fat quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Anh v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/dier-noi-gi-sau-cu-sut-quyet-dinh-dua-dt-anh-vao-tu-ket-world-cup.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia, Eric Dier \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khen ng\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t.</h2><h2>Dier khen ng\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Colombia v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Harry Kane trong hi\u1ec7p hai. Tuy v\u1eady, Colombia c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tay v\u1eeba khi ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede hai hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, Colombia l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n khi t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua th\u00eam b\u00e0n n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Dier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/dier-noi-gi-sau-cu-sut-quyet-dinh-dua-dt-anh-vao-tu-ket-world-cup.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Eric Dier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Colombia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 Eric Dier cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 sau khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua tr\u1edb tr\u00eau v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00eam qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;B\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 h\u00f4m qua l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb suy s\u1ee5p v\u00e0 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng \u00fd ngh\u0129 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh sau b\u00e0n thua v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eadt ra c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n t\u00e2m l\u00fd cho t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Dier chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eric Dier l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1eef nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 penalty th\u1ee9 5 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\" target=\"_blank\">Colombia vs Anh</span> v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn h\u01a1i hi\u1ec1n. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Ospina \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tay v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng may m\u1eafn l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebft l\u1ed9 sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, Dier kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u00fat lo l\u1eafng khi g\u00e1nh tr\u00ean vai tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><em>&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc m\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ghi b\u00e0n sau khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 \u01a1n tr\u1eddi l\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh:</strong><br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\"><em>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-trong-ngay-dt-anh-pha-dop-de-vao-tu-ket-469-190319.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Anh ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-anh-tren-cham-11m-421-190321.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau \u0111\u00eam l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Colombia 1-1 (pen 3-4) Anh (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</em></div>\r\n<em> <br>\r\n<br>\r\n</em>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"872","checkdouble":"190331"},{"date":"07:36 04/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (4/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-472018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; p